  Designer and Developer.
</p>
<h2>
  Problem
</h2>
<p>
  While having demonstrated the efficacy 
  of their products, and gathering attention 
  in one of the most competitive energy 
  markets in the world, Billcap were relying 
  on an ad-hoc communication strategy and 
  thin brand. In order to acquire customers 
  and be treated seriously they needed a 
  clear brand and comms strategy to 
  differentiate themselves from the incumbent
  competitors.
</p>
<p>
  Also, while confident about their 
  proven products there was uncertainty
  about the value of other parts of the 
  platform and how to pitch them.
</p>
