<h2>
  Website
</h2>
<p>
  Armed with the framework I began producing 
  brand assets like the logo, product icons,
  colours palettes, font selections, example 
  layouts, etc. These were then applied 
  to layouts before being applied to a 
  <a href="http://www.billcap.com/">new website</a> 
